href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/concepts/design-and-abstractions/architectural-constructs/vcf-topology/vcf-management-components.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">management components</a> of the&nbsp;<a data-href="VCF Instance" href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/concepts/design-and-abstractions/fleet-and-domain-model/vcf-instance.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">VCF Instance</a> and, for the first VCF Instance,&nbsp;<a data-href="VCF Operations" href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/control-planes/vcf-operations/vcf-operations.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">VCF Operations</a> and&nbsp;<a data-href="VCF Automation" href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/control-planes/vcf-automation/vcf-automation.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">VCF Automation</a>.In addition to the components that are common for each&nbsp;VCF Domain, the management domain includes the&nbsp;
<br><a data-href="SDDC Manager" href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/control-planes/sddc-manager/sddc-manager.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">SDDC Manager</a> <a data-tooltip-position="top" aria-label="Virtual Appliance" data-href="Virtual Appliance" href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/concepts/virtual-appliance/virtual-appliance.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">Appliance</a> and the&nbsp;<a data-href="Fleet Management" href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/control-planes/vcf-operations/platform-operations-and-services/platform-services-and-management/managing-the-cloud/fleet-management.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">Fleet Management</a> <a data-tooltip-position="top" aria-label="Virtual Appliance" data-href="Virtual Appliance" href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/concepts/virtual-appliance/virtual-appliance.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">Appliance</a>, that adds workflows for infrastructure management automation to the&nbsp;<a data-href="VCF Operations" href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/control-planes/vcf-operations/vcf-operations.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">VCF Operations</a> instance for the&nbsp;<a data-href="VCF Fleet" href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/concepts/design-and-abstractions/fleet-and-domain-model/vcf-fleet.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">VCF Fleet</a>.
