Performance-sensitive vs general A VCF Domain is to VCF what a Kubernetes cluster is to Kubernetes-based platforms.It gives you:
Failure domain isolation
Security boundary
Upgrade blast-radius control
Operational independence
Without VCF Domains, everything would be patched, upgraded, and potentially broken together.<br>In <a data-href="VCF Automation" href="./https://vcf.wtf/vcf/control-planes/vcf-automation/vcf-automation.html" class="internal-link" target="_self" rel="noopener nofollow">VCF Automation</a>:
