Events Auditing: Event auditing provides visibility into platform interaction changes across the VCF infrastructure and insights into suspicious access events and policy violations.
Compliance: Ensure compliance for the VCF infrastructure and cloud environments against optimum configurations, maintaining a consistent configuration across SDDC components, reducing organizational and business risk.
